game.name: Princess Wetsuit
game.description:
It is always wonderful to pick up a new outfit and dress you up to impress people around you! And, your craving for wearing cool outfits increases a lot especially when you go outside to enjoy your vacations. The same has happed with the two cute Disney princesses Elsa and Rapunzel, who have planned for a lovely holiday at the seaside. But, they both have forgot to collect their diving suits. Would you help them to sort out this issue? Join Princess Wetsuit game and help princesses to shop for diving suits!

The good news is that they still have a chance to shop for their desired clothing items. Join the princesses to pick up the complete outfits required to enjoy a wonderful swimming underwater in this brand new dressing game! First, choose the girl who you want to go on shopping and then help her to enjoy shopping together. Make sure that the princesses select some trendy and appropriate wetsuits to make them more safe and comfortable. 

Give your chosen princess a nice wetsuit and combine it with an oxygen cylinder, a perfect goggle and a pair of matching underwater shoes! Once you collect wetsuit for the first girl, make sure to help the second princess to grab her complete swimsuit in this html5 princess dress-up game. Our website features a wide collection of popular dress up games that are playable on multiple devices, including mobile phones, computers, as well as iPads and iPhones. Enjoy new dressing games, no download required on atmegame.com!
